ZH: 我昨天买了新床单。
EN: I bought new bedsheets yesterday.

ZH: 这条床单很软。
EN: This bedsheet is very soft.

ZH: 她把床单卷起来放到橱柜里。
EN: She rolled up the bedsheets and put them in the cupboard.

ZH: 这是我最喜欢的床单颜色。
EN: This is my favorite color for bedsheets.

ZH: 他每周都会换一次床单。
EN: He changes his bedsheets once a week.

ZH: 这套床单有两个枕头套。
EN: This set of bedsheets comes with two pillowcases.

ZH: 洗床单时要使用温和的洗涤剂。
EN: Use gentle detergent when washing bedsheets.

ZH: 我们的客房都准备好了床单。
EN: The bedsheets in our guest room are all ready.

ZH: 这些床单是我亲手缝制的。
EN: These bedsheets were sewn by me personally.

ZH: 让我来帮你换床单。
EN: Let me help you change the bedsheets.

ZH: 这套床单已经颜色褪了。
EN: The color of this set of bedsheets has faded.

ZH: 我觉得床单很舒服。
EN: I find the bedsheets very comfortable.

ZH: 床单上有些污渍，需要洗。
EN: There are some stains on the bedsheets that need to be washed.

ZH: 我的妹妹喜欢粉色床单。
EN: My little sister likes pink bedsheets.

ZH: 我弟弟总是在床单上弄脏。
EN: My little brother always manages to get the bedsheets dirty.

ZH: 把床单晾晒在外面可以杀菌。
EN: Hanging the bedsheets outside can kill germs.

ZH: 换床单的时候我总是感觉很放松。
EN: I always feel relaxed when changing the bedsheets.

ZH: 我忘记了在洗衣机里放床单。
EN: I forgot to put the bedsheets in the washing machine.

ZH: 你可以试试这套床单，看看舒不舒服。
EN: You can try this set of bedsheets and see if they are comfortable.

ZH: 酒店的床单都是很干净的。
EN: The bedsheets in hotels are always very clean.
